{"tid":2313333,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"唉 次次到要慶祝 就好大壓力","createTime":"2020-12-05T16:38:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-06T05:20:32.000Z","uid":203579,"like":13,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4b4289de312e9f4efbb7ee6909166c45d51491a6","tid":2313333,"uid":203579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T16:38:20.000Z","msg":"生日要慶我明。<br />\n<br />\n點解周年紀念次撚次都係我諗我出錢？<br />\n拍拖你冇份？ <br />\n<br />\n聖誕個啲乜乜柒柒又expect 我諗，想有驚喜，大佬我真心乜穚都冇曬啦。<br />\n<br />\n有次真係乜都冇，又屌我冇情趣又悶，屌我平時講個啲鳩野你冇笑到？我flirt 你，送野俾你，你冇冧？個啲唔撚係情趣？節日有先係？<br />\n<br />\n要諗真係好大壓力，一年幾次，隔幾個月又驚一次。<br />\n<br />\n唉，個女仔幾好都好，一年幾次壓力測試真係唔掂，好撚想分手。<br />\n<br />\n發洩完 有冇人有同感"},{"pid":"9ab6af87cd5a858a6661bd59153245f1579ca87f","tid":2313333,"uid":20914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T16:41:07.000Z","msg":"你追佢嗰陣都係咁？"},{"pid":"5376aff9a2a6149c5cd8a78eb09b248c4989d5a0","tid":2313333,"uid":282789,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T16:41:59.000Z","msg":"感情問題一律建議分手"},{"pid":"fbea93be4b0fda5f1c793d11fdb39c40d2207aed","tid":2313333,"uid":138731,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T16:43:14.000Z","msg":"屌 點解咁閪既女都有男朋友 自問性格唔差就比人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點撚解 公平咩<br />\n不如都係做閪女人算了"},{"pid":"a9bb268afde91517dbc1aa3f53380164d66694c4","tid":2313333,"uid":203579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ab6af87cd5a858a6661bd59153245f1579ca87f","tid":2313333,"uid":20914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T16:41:07.000Z","msg":"你追佢嗰陣都係咁？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T16:43:59.000Z","msg":"反而冇 好普通"},{"pid":"7356f5fed9eb6dc36cfcca0c09d7b9d8cc8ad8b3","tid":2313333,"uid":369585,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T16:44:00.000Z","msg":"當你準備節目比另一個既時侯 如果你唔係enjoy 你要諗下對方係咪已經唔值你既花咁多心機"},{"pid":"ee6e1c9db9bfb8336c43c31f6195b6540816b2d1","tid":2313333,"uid":203579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"